Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.05,0:48:38.65,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Let's use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.25,0:48:37.92,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,810)}Need to use it. Need to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.92,0:48:38.65,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,810)}Need to use it x2
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.65,0:48:40.38,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}"Let's stay together", everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.02,0:48:48.25,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}We're pretty buried under all the other stamps,\Nbut I really am using mine!
