Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.45,0:54:08.32,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}MEIKO really did work hard in this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.32,0:54:11.05,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Endlessly grateful to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.72,0:54:11.05,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,820)}So grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.05,0:54:12.22,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.22,0:54:13.48,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.48,0:54:15.05,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Haha indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.05,0:54:18.52,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Next up is the trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.52,0:54:21.62,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So good we get to see so many different angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.62,0:54:24.98,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Long-hair MEIKO is so pretty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.98,0:54:27.85,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.85,0:54:30.25,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}The flowers look so good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.12,0:54:30.25,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,820)}They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.25,0:54:32.38,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.38,0:54:35.28,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Let's move to Kanade, untrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.27,0:54:37.39,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,820)}You can do it~
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.28,0:54:39.32,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Uhh... untrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.32,0:54:41.15,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}She's eating her cup ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.15,0:54:43.85,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.85,0:54:47.65,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}That's Kanade's untrained, next we have the trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.15,0:54:51.05,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Her hair is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.05,0:54:52.92,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.92,0:55:02.22,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,50)}Note: Yes yes yes yes please go watch it if you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.92,0:54:59.18,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}By the way, if you haven't checked\Nout Kanade's side story yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.18,0:55:02.22,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I think you might enjoy the story more if you read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.22,0:55:05.82,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}If you've been playing the event\Nand have points saved up,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.82,0:55:08.22,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I think you can still exchange for her up till today,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.22,0:55:10.58,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}so please do get this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.58,0:55:11.52,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Next up,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.52,0:55:11.92,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.92,0:55:12.52,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.52,0:55:14.08,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Mafuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.78,0:55:14.08,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,820)}Mafuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.08,0:55:15.35,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}You long press it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.35,0:55:16.12,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.70,0:55:19.58,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Mafuyu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.58,0:55:23.58,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Mafuyu also helped out a lot this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.58,0:55:30.22,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Right? I was really glad to hear\Nsuch warm words coming from Mafuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.22,0:55:32.92,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I always really like her expressions in these.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.92,0:55:34.65,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Please admire every detail, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.65,0:55:37.75,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Please do, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.75,0:55:38.65,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Aren't these so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.65,0:55:41.18,Ena - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.18,0:55:45.12,Mizuki - Subscreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Last time's illustrations had\Na lot more of a muted palette,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.12,0:55:49.48,Ena,,0,0,0,,but these ones feature a lot more vivid, yet warm and gentle hues.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.48,0:55:51.98,Ena,,0,0,0,,Both have their good points,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.98,0:55:57.78,Ena,,0,0,0,,but I feel like this gentler style really fit the progression of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.78,0:56:01.98,Ena,,0,0,0,,Alright, so with that, it was just a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.98,0:56:07.82,Ena,,0,0,0,,but that's all for the ProSeka Aftertalk "With Our Wounded Hands" Edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.82,0:56:11.22,Ena,,0,0,0,,What did you think, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.22,0:56:17.72,Ena,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching, and for all the warm comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.72,0:56:23.15,Ena,,0,0,0,,With that, we'll each make some closing remarks about today's stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.15,0:56:25.22,Ena,,0,0,0,,Take it away, Hinata-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.22,0:56:29.75,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for watching, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.75,0:56:37.95,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Right. For me, I think that the best way I can "face" Mizuki is through my acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.95,0:56:44.45,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,and while I think it might be a bit presumptuous to say that I fully met her feelings with my acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.45,0:56:50.12,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,I did all that I could to put my absolute everything into recording in that booth that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.12,0:56:57.62,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,And you know... for voice acting in games like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.62,0:57:03.05,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,you have to leave pauses between lines for the player to tap through.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.05,0:57:06.22,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,That's... a pretty common sense way of doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.22,0:57:09.32,Ena,,0,0,0,,The editors would have to cut out each line.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.02,0:57:09.32,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they'd have to cut out each line.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.32,0:57:13.88,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,That'd normally be the case, but for these performances with lots of crying—
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.88,0:57:15.62,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,how to say—
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.62,0:57:18.62,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,you can't really cut yourself short.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.62,0:57:25.22,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,So I asked Colorful Palette if it'd be fine to record this all in one continuous take.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.22,0:57:30.85,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Like, "could you cut this part out?" or "could you cut my crying or sniffling here out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.85,0:57:33.05,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,That way I can keep the emotions flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.05,0:57:34.62,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,And they were very understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.62,0:57:41.42,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,And when I saw the final cut, I thought they did an amazing job following through with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.42,0:57:51.55,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,I could tell that Colorful Palette edited it all together giving lots of care to the emotions I put into my acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.55,0:57:53.98,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,So— how to say—
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.98,0:57:57.25,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Though I am watching over Mizuki as the one voicing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.25,0:58:02.45,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,there's still a lot lying ahead for all the N25 members,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.45,0:58:07.62,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,like their careers, songwriting, and other challenges they'll continue facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.62,0:58:11.42,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,And even if I'm not directly helping them,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.42,0:58:18.25,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,maybe from the shadows, I hope I can continue to quietly support the N25 members.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.25,0:58:21.15,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for watching today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.15,0:58:23.32,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Over to Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.32,0:58:27.02,Ena,,0,0,0,,Ehh, thank you very much everyone for watching all the way to the end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.02,0:58:34.32,Ena,,0,0,0,,For this story— this story and the previous one, especially both Chapter 8s,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.32,0:58:38.22,Ena,,0,0,0,,we received so many comments from those who watched the story and were—
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.22,0:58:45.52,Ena,,0,0,0,,were moved, or how it really gave them pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.52,0:58:54.05,Ena,,0,0,0,,But truly, those moments could only happen because of the long journey these characters have walked to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.05,0:58:59.05,Ena,,0,0,0,,We only watched Chapter 8 today, but if you start from Chapter 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.05,0:59:03.05,Ena,,0,0,0,,the characters are always grappling with issues or challenging themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.05,0:59:04.85,Ena,,0,0,0,,That’s what makes everything possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.85,0:59:08.05,Ena,,0,0,0,,Ena and Mizuki being able to move forward together is, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.05,0:59:14.55,Ena,,0,0,0,,only possible thanks to their bonds and interactions with the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.55,0:59:21.68,Ena,,0,0,0,,So I really hope everyone watches every single chapter without skipping,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.68,0:59:26.75,Ena,,0,0,0,,to truly feel what the characters are going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.75,0:59:31.55,Ena,,0,0,0,,As for Ena's growth, after all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.55,0:59:37.65,Ena,,0,0,0,,Ena was able to get through to Mizuki— maybe not completely yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.65,0:59:43.15,Ena,,0,0,0,,but Ena was able to play this role because she's continuing to challenge herself by facing her painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.15,0:59:46.85,Ena,,0,0,0,,Thanks to all the growth she went through in all the previous stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.85,0:59:50.68,Ena,,0,0,0,,she's mature enough to see things through someone else's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.68,0:59:57.18,Ena,,0,0,0,,and that's what helped both Mizuki and Ena move forward in this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.18,1:00:00.88,Ena,,0,0,0,,N25 were able to face one of their problems together,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.88,1:00:07.58,Ena,,0,0,0,,but for Ena personally, with her painting,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.58,1:00:10.78,Ena,,0,0,0,,she hasn't quite reached her goal yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.78,1:00:13.88,Ena,,0,0,0,,In Ena's last focus event story,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.88,1:00:18.65,Ena,,0,0,0,,there were some comments saying she's gotten over her issues,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.65,1:00:21.08,Ena,,0,0,0,,but personally, I don’t see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.08,1:00:26.85,Ena,,0,0,0,,I feel like this is just the beginning of an endless road towards the artist she's striving to become.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.85,1:00:30.42,Ena,,0,0,0,,So, thank you, truly, to everyone who supports her on that journey.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.42,1:00:37.65,Ena,,0,0,0,,I’ll continue from here forward taking responsibility for Ena’s life,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.65,1:00:40.88,Ena,,0,0,0,,and do my absolute best to carry her life forward as an actor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.88,1:00:41.38,Ena,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.38,1:00:43.02,Ena,,0,0,0,,So with that...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.15,1:00:43.02,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.02,1:00:44.75,Ena,,0,0,0,,that's all we have for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.75,1:00:46.28,Ena,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.28,1:00:54.95,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965.333,170)}Bro if you haven't watch Ena5 yet what the heck are you doing here
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.28,1:00:50.35,Ena,,0,0,0,,Those of you who haven't watched the story, once the next event starts,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.35,1:00:51.85,Ena,,0,0,0,,it'll be on—
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.88,1:00:51.85,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,YouTube?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.85,1:00:53.55,Ena,,0,0,0,,On YouTube?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.55,1:00:54.95,Ena,,0,0,0,,Ah, in-game?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.95,1:01:00.05,Ena,,0,0,0,,You can watch it freely in-game, so please do so if you couldn't unlock it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.05,1:01:02.82,Ena,,0,0,0,,It should also be uploaded to YouTube,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.05,1:01:02.82,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.82,1:01:05.15,Ena,,0,0,0,,so please watch it there if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.15,1:01:08.38,Ena,,0,0,0,,So with that, we're at the end of our program.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.38,1:01:11.38,Ena,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's too early to say "Happy New Year?" For Project Sekai?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.38,1:01:14.75,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,"Happy New Year"...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.75,1:01:17.35,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Well, the staff still have a lot of recording left to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.35,1:01:20.35,Ena,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all the staff we're seeing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.52,1:01:20.35,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Staff members,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.35,1:01:22.95,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,thanks for the continued support. Maybe more fitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.95,1:01:27.45,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,But for everyone watching, we wish you a happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.45,1:01:30.38,Ena,,0,0,0,,On SekaRaji, I said the same thing, thinking it was too early.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.38,1:01:32.18,Ena,,0,0,0,,We just recorded it today.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.18,1:01:36.38,Ena,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, have a happy new year, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.25,1:01:36.38,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Happy new year, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.38,1:01:39.62,Ena,,0,0,0,,We look forward to another great year with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.62,1:01:41.55,Ena,,0,0,0,,See you again next time!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.55,1:01:42.72,Ena,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.25,1:01:45.75,Mizuki,,0,0,0,,Bye bye~
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.72,1:01:45.75,Ena,,0,0,0,,Bye bye~
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.55,1:01:47.55,Ena,,0,0,0,,
